interactions.flavorLineOne: This Seraph Bunker has been hidden under Io for a long time. It is not currently operational. You must push further into the Bunker, clear out enemies and restore power.

This Seraph Bunker has reached Integration Level 1 and you may now claim your first reputation reward. The first 6 integration levels will grant a Powerful reward, the 7th will grant a Pinnacle reward. Beyond that rewards will not be Powerful.
"Rasputin wanted me to tell you: 'This world is protected,'" Ana Bray
Rasputin appreciates your assistance. You've helped him grow in strength so that he might better protect humanity.
This Seraph Bunker has reached Integration Level 7 and you may now claim all Seraph Bunker Rank Bonuses.
"Big Red and I need a hand updating the Seraph Bunker network. Whole system will benefit, we promise." Ana Bray
Rasputin is grateful for your contributions. Take this reward in recognition of your efforts.
